OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Fdry evening and night to come with
OL,7,Fclear spells. The odd light shower
OL,8,Fremains possible in the north and west
OL,9,Fthroughout. Mild for most places and
OL,10,Frather muggy, with some hill fog in
OL,11,Fplaces.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FMorning low cloud will soon
OL,14,Flift and break, to bring plenty of
OL,15,Fsunshine across the region. Perhaps
OL,16,Fthe far northwest at risk of the odd
OL,17,Fafternoon shower. Feeling very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
