OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FTurning
OL,6,Fmore settled into the weekend as high
OL,7,Fpressure starts to build from the
OL,8,Fsouth. Sunny spells and feeling very
OL,9,Fwarm with temperatures well above the
OL,10,FJune average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
